# Annual Security Awareness Training Plan

| Quarter | Topic                          | Format        |
|---------|--------------------------------|---------------|
| Q1      | Phishing & Email Hygiene       | Online Course |
| Q2      | Password Security & MFA        | Live Webinar  |
| Q3      | Secure Remote Work             | PDF Brief     |
| Q4      | Social Engineering & USB Drops | Video Series  |

## Delivery Platforms
- LMS
- Company Intranet
- Phishing Simulators (KnowBe4, Cofense)
